label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡前殖吸虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"前殖吸虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":36,"end":40,"text":"寄生虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":16,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"肠道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"腔上囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":31,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸡前殖吸虫病是由前殖吸虫寄生于鸡的肠道、泄殖腔、腔上囊和输卵管引起的一种寄生虫病。在我国已流行多年，南方地区尤为多见。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"前殖吸虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":21,"text":"卵圆前殖吸虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":22,"end":28,"text":"槐形前殖吸虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":29,"end":35,"text":"透明前殖吸虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 前殖吸虫种类较多。能感染鸡的有卵圆前殖吸虫、槐形前殖吸虫和透明前殖吸虫等。

label: [{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"内部器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":60,"end":66,"text":"透明前殖吸虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"吸虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 虫体扁平较透明，内部器官清晰可见，大小约为5mm×2mm,具有吸盘和小棘，前两种吸虫前端较狭窄，后端宽而圆，外观呈梨形。透明前殖吸虫呈椭圆形。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"前殖吸虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":19,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"腔上囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"直肠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":40,"end":43,"text":"排泄物","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 前殖吸虫发育需要2个中间宿主。成虫在鸡的输卵管、腔上囊或直肠内产卵，虫卵随粪便或排泄物排出体外落入水中后，被第一中间宿主淡水螺吞食，并在其体内孵化为毛蚴。

label: [{"start":1,"end":2,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]}]
text: 当鸡啄食了含有囊蚴的蜻蜓后，就会发生感染。囊蚴在鸡体内发育成为成虫。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡前殖吸虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":34,"text":"食欲不振","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":38,"end":42,"text":"精神萎靡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":43,"end":47,"text":"羽毛粗乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"粗乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":49,"end":58,"text":"蹲伏平地作产蛋姿势","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸡前殖吸虫病在春夏两季多发，病初无明显症状。病情严重时，病鸡食欲不振，消瘦，精神萎靡，羽毛粗乱，常蹲伏平地作产蛋姿势。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"成年病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"产软壳蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"无壳蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"畸形蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":29,"text":"泄殖腔排出蛋壳碎片","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":39,"text":"流出浓稠的白色液体","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":44,"end":48,"text":"腹部膨大","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"膨大","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":49,"end":53,"text":"步态不稳","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":54,"end":58,"text":"两腿叉开","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":59,"end":64,"text":"泄殖腔外翻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":65,"end":69,"text":"充血潮红","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"腹部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":55,"end":56,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":59,"end":62,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"外翻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 成年病鸡产软壳蛋、无壳蛋或畸形蛋，有时从泄殖腔排出蛋壳碎片或流出浓稠的白色液体。有些病鸡腹部膨大，步态不稳，两腿叉开，泄殖腔外翻并充血潮红，严重时可引起死亡。

label: [{"start":5,"end":12,"text":"输卵管黏膜增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":30,"text":"管壁上可找到虫体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":44,"text":"管内有渗出物和残留的蛋物质","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":10,"text":"输卵管黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"管壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"管内","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 剖检时可见输卵管黏膜增厚、充血、发炎或出血，管壁上可找到虫体，管内有渗出物和残留的蛋物质。

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":25,"end":31,"text":"卵黄性腹膜炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"输卵管破裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"破裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 部分病鸡的输卵管因炎症的加剧而导致输卵管破裂，继发卵黄性腹膜炎。

label: [{"start":1,"end":7,"text":"鸡前殖吸虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":29,"end":30,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"排畸形蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":25,"end":28,"text":"变质蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":40,"text":"排泄物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 在鸡前殖吸虫病流行的地区，遇有可疑病鸡或排畸形蛋、变质蛋的鸡时，可取泄殖腔排泄物镜检，观察有无虫卵；或剖检病鸡，若找到虫体即可确诊。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"四氯化碳","labels":["drug"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"鸡只","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":19,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"注射","labels":["control"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"灌服","labels":["control"]},{"start":43,"end":48,"text":"做嗦囊注射","labels":["control"]},{"start":37,"end":40,"text":"植物油","labels":["drug"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"嗦囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"驱虫","labels":["control"]}]
text: (1)四氯化碳。根据鸡只的大小，每只鸡注射或灌服2~3mL,也可以与等量的植物油混合后做嗦囊注射。常用于早期的驱虫。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"丙硫苯咪唑","labels":["drug"]},{"start":25,"end":30,"text":"一次性口服","labels":["control"]}]
text: (2)丙硫苯咪唑。按每千克体重100~120mg,一次性口服。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"硫双二氯酚","labels":["drug"]},{"start":25,"end":30,"text":"一次性口服","labels":["control"]}]
text: (3)硫双二氯酚。按每千克体重200~300mg,一次性口服。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"吡喹酮","labels":["drug"]},{"start":18,"end":23,"text":"一次性口服","labels":["control"]}]
text: (4)吡喹酮。按每千克体重60mg,一次性口服。

label: [{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"有计划的驱虫","labels":["control"]},{"start":23,"end":24,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":32,"text":"防止鸡啄食蜻蜓及其幼虫","labels":["control"]},{"start":75,"end":82,"text":"使用化学杀虫剂","labels":["control"]},{"start":77,"end":82,"text":"化学杀虫剂","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 在流行地区，可在春夏季节进行有计划的驱虫。防止鸡啄食蜻蜓及其幼虫，在蜻蜓出没的季节，勿在清晨、傍晚以及雨后到池塘边放牧，以防发生感染。有条件的地区，可使用化学杀虫剂消灭第一中间宿主。
